sentences: Rydah J. Klyde is a Bay Area rapper from Pittsburg, California best known for his affiliation with the rap group Mob Figaz.
Around 2002, Rydah signed a solo deal with Mac Dre's Thizz Entertainment label.
In 2003, he released his album Tha Fly Gangsta.
